Rombus - Wow, thanks for the insight!  OMG, I see now that I am completely wrong and you are completely right!  Your well reasoned argument for why I am wrong is just amazing!  Tell me again though why I should just sit there quietly and heal the wizard when the wizard is chaining nukes not using concussion and tanking 50% of the time, making the mob a ping-pong ball?  I suppose you would say I was a nitpicking ass if the warrior was shooting arrows at the mob the entire fight instead of taunting and meleeing and I had the *AUDACITY* to criticize them for it.  Why don't you wait to open your mouth until you actually have something to say?<br>
